* 1.0.0
	– TYPO3 11.5 support only
	– JavaScript fix for one column layout
	– BREAKING CHANGES
		– No more pagination widget but requires t3brightside/paginatedprocessors
		– Changes in pagination XML in Templates/Gallerycontent.html
		– SQL to migrate yourself:
			– tx_gallerycontent_pagination to tx_paginatedprocessors_paginationenabled
			– tx_gallerycontent_paginateitems to tx_paginatedprocessors_itemsperpage
